  "keyFeatures": [
    "Point cloud filtering (VoxelGrid, PassThrough, Statistical Outlier Removal, radius-based filtering)",
    "3D feature descriptors (FPFH, VFH, SHOT, NARF, PFH, spin images)",
    "Point cloud registration (ICP, NDT, GICP, RANSAC-based initial alignment)",
    "Segmentation algorithms (Euclidean clustering, region growing, SAC, supervoxels)",
    "Surface reconstruction (Greedy Projection, Poisson, MLS resampling, Marching Cubes)",
    "I/O support for PCD, PLY, OBJ, PNG, and sensor grabbers (OpenNI, RealSense, Kinect, LiDAR)",
    "KdTree and Octree spatial data structures for efficient neighbor search",
    "3D visualization via PCLVisualizer (VTK-based) and CloudViewer",
    "GPU/CUDA acceleration for select algorithms",
    "Support for custom PointT types via template metaprogramming"
  ],
